text.tspan: This wall has two windows and a corridor. The windows on all walls are in the same
locations. This is the inside point of view for Section A or outside view for Section B,
East/West Wall - Targets centered under windows on inside of arena
The hall should align with the room walls. Safety net is outside of arena at target zone.
This wall is the West wall of the A section and the East wall of the B section .
